node.text: Here I show you guys exactly how I load my bike into my truck without any help. With the right technique and a little practice, this can be just as easy for you! Note: not all bikes have an idle adjustment but you can install one on most of them or simply use the throttle to add a little gas on the way up the ramp. Enjoy! 😁 Brought to you by @russbrownmotorcycleattorneys #russbrownmotorcycleattorneys
